<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px 30px; text-indent: -30px; font-weight: normal; font-size: 10px; line-height: normal; font-family: Verdana; -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #000000;"><span style="font-kerning: none;">9.1 We may revise this Privacy Policy from time to time.</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px 30px; text-indent: -30px; font-weight: normal; font-size: 10px; line-height: normal; font-family: Verdana; -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #000000;"><span style="font-kerning: none;">9.2 You should check this space regularly to ensure You are aware and happy with any changes to the Privacy Policy. The amended Privacy Policy takes effect from the date of publication of the amended Privacy Policy on this space, and You hereby waive any right You may otherwise have to be notified of, or to consent to, revisions of this Privacy Policy. You agree that You are responsible for regularly checking this space for any updates, amendments, or changes in relation to the Privacy Policy.</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px 30px; text-indent: -30px; font-weight: normal; font-size: 10px; line-height: normal; font-family: Verdana; -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #000000;"><span style="font-kerning: none;">9.3 You further agree that any further use that You make in connection with the Service after the effective date of the amended Privacy Policy will constitute Your binding acceptance to any such amended Policy. If You do not agree to be bound by the revised Privacy Policy, You must stop using the Service.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-weight: normal; font-size: 10px; line-height: normal; font-family: Verdana; -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #000000;"><span style="font-kerning: none;"><strong>10. Analytics</strong></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px 30px; text-indent: -30px; font-weight: normal; font-size: 10px; line-height: normal; font-family: Verdana; -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #000000;"><span style="font-kerning: none;">10.1 We use a tool called &ldquo;Google Analytics&rdquo; to collect information about use of Our Service and Website. Google Analytics is a web analytics tool that helps Us understand how users and/or visitors engage with our Website and/or Service. Google Analytics collects information such as how often users visit Our Website and/or Service, what pages or sections they visit when they do so, or the demographic distribution of visitors and/or users of Our Website and Service. Additionally, information about your computer, including your IP address, operating system and browser type, may be collected in order to produce aggregate insights and create reports and/or statistical data without identifying individual visitors or users. Such reports and statistical data helps in identifying possible ways of improving our Website and Service for Our users. For information about the privacy practices of Google Analytics, you can visit <a href="https://www.google.com/policies/privacy/"><span style="font-size: 10px; line-height: normal; -webkit-font-kerning: none;">https://www.google.com/policies/privacy/</span></a> and <a href="http://www.google.com/policies/privacy/partners/"><span style="font-size: 10px; line-height: normal; -webkit-font-kerning: none;">http://www.google.com/policies/privacy/partners/</span></a>. If you elect to opt-out of data collection by Google Analytics (to the extent available) and subsequently use the Service through a different device or otherwise change your cookie or privacy settings on your device, you will need to opt-out again.</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-weight: normal; font-size: 10px; line-height: normal; font-family: Verdana; -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #000000;"><span style="font-kerning: none;"><strong>11. Your rights</strong></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px 30px; text-indent: -30px; font-weight: normal; font-size: 10px; line-height: normal; font-family: Verdana; -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #000000;"><span style="font-kerning: none;">11.1 The Company will comply with individual&rsquo;s requests regarding access, correction, and/or deletion of the personal data it stores in accordance with applicable law.&nbsp;</span></p>
